<h2 id=3D"what-is-number-picker-wheel?" class=3D"StyledHeading-sc-1rdh4aw-0=
 dxYuao">1. What is Number Picker Wheel?</h2>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">Number Picker Wheel is a ra=
ndom number generator (RNG) tool used to pick a random number by spinning t=
he wheel. This is another specialized spinner of <a href=3D"https://pickerw=
heel.com/" class=3D"PickerWheelManual__Anchor-sc-1nyvcuw-0 gexkKc">Picker W=
heel</a> focusing on a number generator.</p>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">There are two result mode t=
hat you can choose for your application.
<span class=3D"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper" style=3D"position:relative;displa=
y:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;max-width:474px">
