<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">The Random Number result mo=
de is based on range or formula input methods. This is useful when you only=
 need less than 1000 (Desktop/Tablet) or 500 (Mobile) different numbers. Yo=
u can't put more than these numbers due to the size limitation of the wheel=
. By default, it is a 10 value spinner.
