<h2 id=3D"wheel-customization?" class=3D"StyledHeading-sc-1rdh4aw-0 dxYuao"=
>3. Wheel Customization?</h2>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">The wheel can be customized=
 or configured in a variety of ways to match different use cases.</p>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">You can easily do this in t=
he Tool Settings section (below the wheel section). The tool settings is lo=
cated at: (click to expand)
