<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">The following settings can =
be changed:</p>
<ul>
<li>Spin Behavior
<ul>
<li>Spinning speed (lvl1 to lv10).</li>
<li>Spinning duration (1s to 30s).</li>
<li>Enable manual stop button.</li>
<li>Mystery spin (replace inputs on wheels with =E2=80=9C?=E2=80=9D)</li>
<li>Spin count</li>
<li>Random initial angle.</li>
<li>Initial Spinning</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Confetti &amp; Sound
<ul>
<li>Disable/Enable confetti.</li>
<li>Sound on/off.</li>
<li>Customize starting, spinning, and ending sounds.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Tool Colors - Change the wheel colors with several themes provided.</li=
>
<li>Background Color - Change the background color of the whole section.</l=
i>
<li>Background Image - Add a background image at the wheel section. <strong=
>(Premium Users)</strong></li>
<li>Spin Button - Customize your own spin button. <strong>(Premium Users)</=
strong></li>
<li>Banner | Logo - Adding your own logo or banner. <strong>(Premium Users)=
</strong></li>
</ul>
