    </span></p>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">For logged-in users, you ha=
ve more benefits for the file storage.</p>
<ul>
<li>You can save more than 1 file. <strong>(Free Users - 7 Files available,=
 Premium Users - Up to 100)</strong></li>
<li>You can access your file with any device anywhere anytime.</li>
<li>Feeling peace of mind without worrying the data loss.</li>
</ul>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD">There are two types of file=
 in Number Picker Wheel which are "List" type and "Share" type.</p><div id=
=3D"AdThrive_Content_12_tablet" class=3D"adthrive-ad adthrive-content adthr=
ive-content-12 adthrive-ad-cls" style=3D"min-height: 250px;"></div>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD"><strong>List type</strong> =
- This is the file type you will see after saving your list of data. This i=
s private and only you can open and edit.</p>
<p class=3D"StyledParagraph-sc-tbetod-0 ggSFeD"><strong>Share type</strong>=
 - Once you create a share link from any private List file, the file now be=
comes a Share file, it is viewable/copyable by others, but only you have pe=
rmission to edit. The process of converting a List file to a Share file is =
irreversible.</p>
